{
  "info": {
    "name": "JobLoom API",
    "description": "Complete API documentation for JobLoom Backend - A rural employment platform with comprehensive review and rating system.\n\n## Features\n- User Management (Registration, Login, Profile)\n- Job Listings\n- Applications\n- Review & Rating System with Trust Scores\n- Health Check Endpoints\n\n## Authentication\nMost endpoints require JWT Bearer token authentication. Register/Login to get a token.\n\n## Base URL\n`http://localhost:3000/api`\n\n## Environment Variables\n- `{{baseUrl}}` - API base URL (default: http://localhost:3000/api)\n- `{{token}}` - JWT authentication token",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    {
      "key": "baseUrl",
      "value": "http://localhost:3000/api",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "token",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Health & Status",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "API Root",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "http://localhost:3000/",
              "protocol": "http",
              "host": ["localhost"],
              "port": "3000",
              "path": [""]
            },
            "description": "Get API information and available endpoints"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Health Check",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "http://localhost:3000/health",
              "protocol": "http",
              "host": ["localhost"],
              "port": "3000",
              "path": ["health"]
            },
            "description": "Comprehensive health check with database, memory, and system info"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Liveness Probe",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "http://localhost:3000/healthz",
              "protocol": "http",
              "host": ["localhost"],
              "port": "3000",
              "path": ["healthz"]
            },
            "description": "Kubernetes liveness probe - checks if server is running"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Readiness Probe",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "http://localhost:3000/ready",
              "protocol": "http",
              "host": ["localhost"],
              "port": "3000",
              "path": ["ready"]
            },
            "description": "Kubernetes readiness probe - checks if server can handle requests"
          }
        }
      ],
      "description": "Health check and monitoring endpoints"
    },
    {
      "name": "Authentication & Users",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Register User",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 201) {",
                  "    const jsonData = pm.response.json();",
                  "    pm.environment.set('token', jsonData.data.token);",
                  "    pm.environment.set('userId', jsonData.data.user._id);",
                  "}"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"firstName\": \"John\",\n  \"lastName\": \"Doe\",\n  \"email\": \"john.doe@example.com\",\n  \"password\": \"SecurePass123!\",\n  \"role\": \"job_seeker\",\n  \"phone\": \"+94771234567\",\n  \"location\": {\n    \"village\": \"Galle Face\",\n    \"district\": \"Colombo\",\n    \"province\": \"Western\"\n  }\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/users/register",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["users", "register"]
            },
            "description": "Register a new user account.\n\n**Roles:**\n- `job_seeker` - Looking for jobs\n- `employer` - Posting jobs\n- `admin` - Platform administrator\n\n**Password Requirements:**\n- Minimum 8 characters\n- At least one uppercase, lowercase, number\n\n**Returns:** User object and JWT token"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Verify Registration",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"phone\": \"+94771234567\",\n  \"otp\": \"123456\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/users/verify-registration",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["users", "verify-registration"]
            },
            "description": "Verify user registration with OTP sent via SMS."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Login",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                  "    const jsonData = pm.response.json();",
                  "    pm.environment.set('token', jsonData.data.token);",
                  "    pm.environment.set('userId', jsonData.data.user._id);",
                  "}"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"john.doe@example.com\",\n  \"password\": \"SecurePass123!\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/users/login",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["users", "login"]
            },
            "description": "Authenticate user and receive JWT token.\n\n**Returns:** User object and JWT token (valid for 7 days)"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Forgot Password",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"phone\": \"+94771234567\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/users/forgot-password",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["users", "forgot-password"]
            },
            "description": "Send password reset OTP to user's phone."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Verify Password Reset",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"phone\": \"+94771234567\",\n  \"otp\": \"123456\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/users/verify-password-reset",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["users", "verify-password-reset"]
            },
            "description": "Verify password reset OTP and receive a reset token."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Reset Password",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"phone\": \"+94771234567\",\n  \"resetToken\": \"your_reset_token\",\n  \"password\": \"NewSecurePass123!\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/users/reset-password",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["users", "reset-password"]
            },
            "description": "Reset user password using the reset token."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Get User by ID",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{token}}"
              }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/users/profile/:id",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["users", "profile", ":id"],
              "variable": [
                {
                  "key": "id",
                  "value": "{{userId}}"
                }
              ]
            },
            "description": "Get user profile by user ID.\n\n**Requires:** JWT token"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Get My Profile",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{token}}"
              }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/users/me",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["users", "me"]
            },
            "description": "Get authenticated user's profile.\n\n**Requires:** JWT token\n\n**Returns:** Complete user profile including private fields"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Update Profile",
          "request": {
            "method": "PUT",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{token}}"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "formdata",
              "formdata": [
                {
                  "key": "firstName",
                  "value": "John",
                  "type": "text"
                },
                {
                  "key": "lastName",
                  "value": "Doe",
                  "type": "text"
                },
                {
                  "key": "phone",
                  "value": "+94771234567",
                  "type": "text"
                },
                {
                  "key": "cv",
                  "description": "Upload one or more CVs",
                  "type": "file",
                  "src": []
                },
                {
                  "key": "profileImage",
                  "description": "Upload profile image",
                  "type": "file",
                  "src": []
                },
                {
                  "key": "skills",
                  "value": "[\"Farming\", \"Driving\"]",
                  "type": "text"
                },
                {
                  "key": "experience",
                  "value": "[{\"title\": \"Farm Worker\", \"company\": \"Green Acres\", \"duration\": \"2 years\"}]",
                  "type": "text"
                },
                {
                  "key": "location",
                  "value": "{\"village\": \"Updated Village\", \"district\": \"Colombo\", \"province\": \"Western\"}",
                  "type": "text"
                }
              ]
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/users/profile",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["users", "profile"]
            },
            "description": "Update authenticated user's profile with multiple CVs, skills, experience, and location.\n\n**Requires:** JWT token\n\n**Fields:**\n- `firstName`, `lastName`, `phone`\n- `cv` (file field, supports up to 5 files)\n- `profileImage` (file field)\n- `skills` (JSON string array, e.g. `[\"skill1\", \"skill2\"]`)\n- `experience` (JSON string array of objects, e.g. `[{\"title\": \"...\", \"company\": \"...\"}]`)\n- `location` (JSON string object, e.g. `{\"village\": \"...\", \"district\": \"...\"}`)"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Delete Account",
          "request": {
            "method": "DELETE",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{token}}"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"password\": \"SecurePass123!\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/users/account",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["users", "account"]
            },
            "description": "Deactivate authenticated user's account."
          }
        }
      ],
      "description": "User registration, authentication, and profile management"
    },
    {
      "name": "Reviews & Ratings",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Create Review",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 201) {",
                  "    const jsonData = pm.response.json();",
                  "    pm.environment.set('reviewId', jsonData.data.review._id);",
                  "}"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{token}}"
              },
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"revieweeId\": \"675c9d4c8e9a1b2c3d4e5f67\",\n  \"jobId\": \"675c9d4c8e9a1b2c3d4e5f68\",\n  \"reviewerType\": \"job_seeker\",\n  \"rating\": 5,\n  \"comment\": \"Excellent employer! Paid on time and good working conditions.\",\n  \"workQuality\": 5,\n  \"communication\": 5,\n  \"punctuality\": 5,\n  \"paymentOnTime\": 5\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/reviews",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["reviews"]
            },
            "description": "Create a new review for an employer or job seeker.\n\n**Requires:** JWT token + Accepted application\n\n**Reviewer Types:**\n- `job_seeker` - Review employer\n- `employer` - Review job seeker\n\n**Rating Criteria (1-5):**\n- `workQuality` - Quality of work\n- `communication` - Communication skills\n- `punctuality` - Timeliness\n- `paymentOnTime` - Payment punctuality (for employers)\n\n**Validation:**\n- Must have worked together (accepted application)\n- Cannot review yourself\n- One review per job per person\n- Can only review within job context"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Get Review by ID",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/reviews/:id",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["reviews", ":id"],
              "variable": [
                {
                  "key": "id",
                  "value": "{{reviewId}}"
                }
              ]
            },
            "description": "Get a single review by its ID.\n\n**Returns:** Complete review with populated user and job data"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Get User Reviews",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/reviews/user/:userId?page=1&limit=10&reviewerType=job_seeker&sort=-createdAt",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["reviews", "user", ":userId"],
              "query": [
                {
                  "key": "page",
                  "value": "1",
                  "description": "Page number"
                },
                {
                  "key": "limit",
                  "value": "10",
                  "description": "Results per page"
                },
                {
                  "key": "reviewerType",
                  "value": "job_seeker",
                  "description": "Filter by reviewer type"
                },
                {
                  "key": "sort",
                  "value": "-createdAt",
                  "description": "Sort field (- for desc)"
                }
              ],
              "variable": [
                {
                  "key": "userId",
                  "value": "{{userId}}"
                }
              ]
            },
            "description": "Get all reviews for a specific user.\n\n**Query Parameters:**\n- `page` - Page number (default: 1)\n- `limit` - Results per page (default: 10)\n- `reviewerType` - Filter by type (job_seeker/employer)\n- `sort` - Sort by field (e.g., -createdAt for newest first)\n\n**Returns:** Paginated review list with metadata"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Get Job Reviews",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/reviews/job/:jobId",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["reviews", "job", ":jobId"],
              "variable": [
                {
                  "key": "jobId",
                  "value": ""
                }
              ]
            },
            "description": "Get all reviews related to a specific job.\n\n**Returns:** Reviews from both employers and job seekers for this job"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Get User Rating Statistics",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/reviews/stats/:userId",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["reviews", "stats", ":userId"],
              "variable": [
                {
                  "key": "userId",
                  "value": "{{userId}}"
                }
              ]
            },
            "description": "Get comprehensive rating statistics for a user.\n\n**Returns:**\n- Average rating (weighted)\n- Total reviews\n- Rating distribution\n- Trust score (0-100)\n- Badge (Elite, Top Rated, Trusted, Rising Star)\n- Criteria breakdown (work quality, communication, etc.)\n- Rating level (Excellent, Very Good, etc.)\n\n**Trust Score Algorithm:**\n- Based on average rating, review count, and completeness\n- Range: 0-100\n- Factors: consistency, volume, detail\n\n**Badges:**\n- **Elite**: 4.8+ rating, 20+ reviews\n- **Top Rated**: 4.5+ rating, 10+ reviews\n- **Trusted**: 4.0+ rating, 5+ reviews\n- **Rising Star**: 4.0+ rating, 2-4 reviews"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Get Employer Reviews",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/reviews/employer/:employerId",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["reviews", "employer", ":employerId"],
              "variable": [
                {
                  "key": "employerId",
                  "value": ""
                }
              ]
            },
            "description": "Get all reviews for an employer (alias for user reviews)."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Get Job Seeker Reviews",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/reviews/jobseeker/:jobSeekerId",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["reviews", "jobseeker", ":jobSeekerId"],
              "variable": [
                {
                  "key": "jobSeekerId",
                  "value": ""
                }
              ]
            },
            "description": "Get all reviews for a job seeker (alias for user reviews)."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Update Review",
          "request": {
            "method": "PUT",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{token}}"
              },
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"rating\": 4,\n  \"comment\": \"Updated review: Good experience overall.\",\n  \"workQuality\": 4,\n  \"communication\": 4,\n  \"punctuality\": 5\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/reviews/:id",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["reviews", ":id"],
              "variable": [
                {
                  "key": "id",
                  "value": "{{reviewId}}"
                }
              ]
            },
            "description": "Update your own review.\n\n**Requires:** JWT token + Review ownership\n\n**Restrictions:**\n- Can only update own reviews\n- Can only update within 7 days of creation\n- Cannot change reviewee or job\n\n**Updatable Fields:**\n- rating, comment\n- workQuality, communication, punctuality, paymentOnTime"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Delete Review",
          "request": {
            "method": "DELETE",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{token}}"
              }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/reviews/:id",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["reviews", ":id"],
              "variable": [
                {
                  "key": "id",
                  "value": "{{reviewId}}"
                }
              ]
            },
            "description": "Delete (soft delete) your own review.\n\n**Requires:** JWT token + Review ownership\n\n**Note:** This is a soft delete - review is marked as deleted but data is retained for moderation."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Report Review",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{token}}"
              },
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"reason\": \"This review contains false information and inappropriate language.\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/reviews/:id/report",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["reviews", ":id", "report"],
              "variable": [
                {
                  "key": "id",
                  "value": "{{reviewId}}"
                }
              ]
            },
            "description": "Report a review for moderation.\n\n**Requires:** JWT token\n\n**Reasons for Reporting:**\n- False information\n- Inappropriate language\n- Personal attacks\n- Spam or abuse\n\n**Restrictions:**\n- Cannot report own reviews\n- One report per user per review\n- Reports are reviewed by moderators"
          }
        }
      ],
      "description": "Complete review and rating system with trust scores, badges, and moderation"
    },
